<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
      Hey there, <%= @instructor.name %>! You have a new course assignment pending for <%= @course.organization.name %>:
      <br/><br/>
      Course Name: <%= @course.name %><br/>
      Location: <%= @course.location_name %><br/>
      Dates: <%= @course.date_string %><br/>
      <br/>
      Visit the following link to accept:
      http://<%= @course.organization.subname %>.enrollex.org/courses/<%= @course.id %>/<%= @course.lowname %>/accept?uuid=<%= @uuid %>
      <br/><br/>
      And you can go here for more info:
      http://<%= @course.organization.subname %>.enrollex.org/catalog?tab=shifts
      <br/><br/>
      <strong>Please respond in <%= @course.organization.instructorShiftExpiryHours %> hours or your priority for this shift will be forfeit.
  </body>
</html>
